'''The Black Cat''' is a cross-platform community [[Special:MyLanguage/world|world]] uploaded by spookyghostboo in 2019. The Black Cat, among the creator's other worlds, is enrolled in the [[Special:MyLanguage/Creator Economy|Creator Economy]] program and features a [[Special:MyLanguage/Creator_Economy#VRChat_Credits|VRChat Credit]] kiosk to add flairs over your [[Special:MyLanguage/avatar|avatar]], even edit the map's theme, and get other perks. The world is a bar and lounge, with many rooms, a second story, and an air ventilation duct system to crawl through.
</div>
[[File:TheBlackCat.png|thumb|The Black Cat's Haupthalle.]]

<span id="Rooms"></span>
==Räume==

Nach dem Beitreten der Black Cat Welt wirst du dich in einem Eingangsraum voller Community-Poster wiederfinden, die von anderen Nutzern eingereicht wurden. Mit ein paar Schritten befindest du dich schon beim Empfang des Black Cat, der ausgestattet ist mit einem Schreibtisch, Computer, zwei Couches und einem kleinen VRChat-Kiosk, der genutzt werden kann, um den Ersteller der Welt mit VRChat-Credits zu unterstützen. Den Flur herunterspaziert, befindest du dich schon im nächsten Raum, der auf zwei Toiletten abzweigt und dem Herzen der Welt, dem Barbereich. Neben einer Bar ist dieser Bereich mit einer Bühne, mehreren Kabinen ausgestattet, die mit Tischen und Stühlen versehen sind, und [[Special:MyLanguage/Mirror|Spiegeln]] . Im Barbereich findest du auch mehrere Objekte, mit denen du interagieren kannst. Dazu gehören beispielsweise: Getränke, eine Gans, eine Flasche Sirup usw. In den zwei Toiletten findest du mehrere Toilettenkabinen, einen Sessel, eine Marmortheke ausgestattet mit Waschbecken und selbstverständlich einen weiteren [[Special:MyLanguage/Mirror|Spiegel]]. Aus dem Kern der Welt herausspaziert, gelangst du über die Treppen in die obere Lounge der Welt oder zu einem weiteren Flur.

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Down the hallway, there is a kitchen with several dishware props to pick up, as well as food. Going left will enter you into a stairwell with a cart to try on a black cat avatar. Proceeding up either set of stairs will lead into a room with a second bar, another stage, and another mirror. In the wall near the stage, there is an air duct that can be opened given it is unlocked, and anyone can crawl inside and access different vents above the main floor that lead to the other rooms of The Black Cat. There is a locked door that leads into a smaller balcony area that overlooks the second story, and stairwell.
</div>

<span id="World_interaction"></span>
==Weltinteraktion==

[[File:HalloweenBlackCat2023.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">The Black Cat Halloween decorations 2023 in the main hall.</span>]]

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The Black Cat is actively maintained by its author, with frequent updates in response to events throughout the year. The world adapts to various holidays such as Halloween and Christmas, changing its decorations accordingly each year.
</div>

<span id="Customization"></span>
===Anpassung===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
A key aspect of The Black Cat's charm is the customization options:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* Users can change the "Goose" item for free, equipping it with different variants.
* People can add flairs above their nametag.
* Some parts of the world can be unlocked.
</div>

<span id="Secret_doors"></span>
===Geheime Türen===

[[File:BlackCatSecretDoors.webp|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">One of the Doors that can be opened and leads to the void.</span>]]

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
At Tier 1, users can unlock secret doors throughout The Black Cat. Upon opening these doors, players will fall into a deep, dark void and be teleported to different areas within the world.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
When teleported, players may find themselves in areas '''not accessible through normal means''', such as a secret corridor (that appears to be located outside on the street?).
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
This area is unique to the secret doors and cannot be accessed from other parts of the world. However, players who are transported to these areas will eventually be randomly teleported back to another location within The Black Cat after a few seconds.
</div>

<span id="Supporters_benefits"></span>
==Supporter-Vorteile==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Supporters benefits using the [[Special:MyLanguage/Creator Economy|Creator Economy]] are available in The Black Cat, allowing users to have access to exclusive features, and sharing them with the entire instance!
</div>

<span id="Tier_1_Supporters"></span>
===Tier 1 Supporter===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
With a Tier 1 Supporter role, users can unlock doors and items for the entire instance. This includes:
* Unlocking the Kitchen doors and accessing the Kitchen.
* Unlocking the balcony door and accessing the balcony upstairs.
* Unlocking vents for access across the entire world.
* Unlocking silly mirrors.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Additionally, users with Supporter role will have their name displayed on the supporter plaque.
</div>

<span id="Tier_2_Supporters"></span>
===Tier 2 Supporter===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
At Tier 2, supporters can benefit from:
* Locally modified speed and jumps values.
</div>

<span id="Tier_3_Supporters"></span>
===Tier 3 Supporter===

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Tier 3 supporters gain access to:
* The video player.
* All world decorations.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
Note that some decorations are free and can be changed by anyone.
</div>

== Merch ==
Vom 20. März bis zum 11. April 2025 lief eine Kampagne, bei der offizielles Merch für "the Black Cat" in Form von kleinen Anstecknadeln veröffentlicht wurde.

